overview: Keri Windsor a beautiful stripper, falls victim to a macabre mugging and narrowly escapes with her life...or does she? John (Evan Stone) a lost soul desperate for a new lease on life, gambles on the one woman he thins can give it to him...but can she? Syren, a free spirit lost to a confluence of astral projection and carnal lust, lures Keri into her perfectly laid plans to recover her soul...but will she? The truth is somewhere...in between.
title: Touch Me
